{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:09.036Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/449\n\n## Problem (contract drift)\n`pm contracts --json` advertises extension_contracts.policy_modes = [\"off\",\"warn\",\"enforce\"] (same for trust_modes), but governance config keys (e.g. governance-workflow-enforcement) accept `strict`, not `enforce`. Agents driving config from contracts construct invalid writes — exactly the drift class pm contracts exists to prevent.\n\n## Proposed fix\nSingle source of truth for mode tokens shared by contracts and config validation; either rename config token to `enforce` (with alias) or fix contracts to advertise `strict`; add a drift spec that walks advertised enum tokens through the real validators.\n\n## Definition of done\nAdvertised policy/trust mode tokens are accepted verbatim by config set; drift spec pins contracts<->validator parity; contracts:update run."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-kjbh"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-449: contracts policy_modes advertises 'enforce' but governance config accepts 'strict' (contract drift)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-449: pm contracts advertises policy_modes [off,warn,enforce] but config validation requires 'strict' — agents driving config from contracts hard-fail. Duplicate check: searched policy modes/enforce strict — no existing item."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:contracts","bug","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:09.036Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:09.036Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":60},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Advertised policy/trust mode tokens are accepted verbatim by pm config set; drift spec walks every advertised enum through the real validator; contracts:update run"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-5k4v"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"ae2aed17bfe5016f055ad522bb120379a400be256f19141b4fb0a05f1b190be7","message":""}
